OL,3,CPrince of Wales set to sell a fifth of
OL,4,CDuchy of Cornwall in next 10 years
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales is set to sell 20%
OL,7,Fof the Duchy of Cornwall in the next
OL,8,F10 years.
OL,10,FPrince William will sell a fifth of
OL,11,Fthe duchy as he plans to invest #500
OL,12,Fmillion in tackling housing and nature
OL,13,Fcrises, The Times first reported.
OL,15,FAs heir to the throne, the Prince of
OL,16,FWales inherited the estate ` a
OL,17,Fportfolio of land, property and
OL,18,Finvestments valued at more than #1
OL,19,Fbillion ` when his father became King.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
