OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779106274
OL,3,CPrince of Wales set to sell a fifth of
OL,4,CDuchy of Cornwall in next 10 years
OL,6,FThe duchy provides William, who is the
OL,7,F25th Duke of Cornwall, with a private
OL,8,Fincome of nearly #23 million a year.
OL,10,FThe money is used to fund the
OL,11,Fcharitable, private and official lives
OL,12,Fof William, the Princess of Wales and
OL,13,Ftheir children, Prince George,
OL,14,FPrincess Charlotte and Prince Louis.
OL,16,FThe prince will consolidate his
OL,17,Fholdings around five geographic
OL,18,F"heartlands", focusing on the Isles of
OL,19,FScilly, Cornwall, Dartmoor, the Bath
OL,20,Farea and Kennington, south London, The
OL,21,FTimes reported.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
