FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779106274
OL,3,CPrince of Wales set to sell a fifth of
OL,4,CDuchy of Cornwall in next 10 years
OL,6,FWill Bax, chief executive of the Duchy
OL,7,Fof Cornwall, told The Times that
OL,8,FWilliam decided the duchy "shouldn't
OL,9,Fjust exist to own land. It should
OL,10,Ffirst and foremost exist to have a
OL,11,Fpositive impact on the world".
OL,13,FMr Bax said of the plan to sell off
OL,14,Fabout a fifth of the duchy estate: "If
OL,15,Fwe don't see an opportunity for
OL,16,Fpositive impact, then perhaps we don't
OL,17,Fneed to be a part of that place.
OL,26,@pD@[OUsD@]O]vD@dOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779106274
OL,3,CPrince of Wales set to sell a fifth of
OL,4,CDuchy of Cornwall in next 10 years
OL,6,F"But where there is social need and
OL,7,Fwhere there is environmental challenge
OL,8,Fand where there is an opportunity to
OL,9,Fenable change, then we'll be a great
OL,10,Fpartner in working with people to
OL,11,Fachieve that."
OL,13,FMr Bax said the prince planned to
OL,14,Finvest #500 million, made up from land
OL,15,Fsales, development income,
OL,16,Fpartnerships and borrowing, into his
OL,17,Fpriorities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]
