CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779106274
OL,3,CPrince of Wales set to sell a fifth of
OL,4,CDuchy of Cornwall in next 10 years
OL,6,FIn March this year, tenants of the
OL,7,FDuchy of Cornwall said they had been
OL,8,Fleft "enormously stressed" following
OL,9,Fplans to sell off land on an estate in
OL,10,FDevon.
OL,12,FThe Bradninch estate, near Cullompton,
OL,13,Fhas been part of the duchy for
OL,14,Fcenturies.
OL,16,FMr Bax told The Times all 10 tenants
OL,17,Fwere "engaged in a conversation around
OL,18,Fbuying their farm" and he believes the
OL,19,Fmajority of them would.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@ZO]yD@FOUzD@RO]
